            "title": "滙豐亦裁員？擬裁減法國348個職位　佔當地一成人手",
            "description": "<div class=\"caas-body\"><figure class=\"caas-figure\"><div class=\"caas-figure-with-pb\" style=\"max-height: 640px\"><div><div class=\"caas-img-container\" style=\"padding-bottom:67%\"><img alt=\"滙豐裁減法國348個職位，佔當地10%員工。(資料圖片)\" class=\"caas-img has-preview\" data-src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/A3GIdfbMCL0dVE3M17kuZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/f053c4badbb14f43edac91985de06f45\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/A3GIdfbMCL0dVE3M17kuZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/f053c4badbb14f43edac91985de06f45\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image\"><figcaption class=\"caption-collapse\">滙豐裁減法國348個職位，佔當地10%員工。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p><span><span><span><span><span>滙豐控股(港交所：005)宣布，計劃在法國透過自願離職計劃裁減348個職位，佔法國員工總數比例約10%。此項裁員行動是行政總裁艾橋智(Georges Elhedery) 推動的節流計劃一部分，目標在2026年底前減少18億美元開支。</span></span></span></span></span></p><figure class=\"caas-figure\"><div class=\"caas-figure-with-pb\" style=\"max-height: 540px\"><div><div class=\"caas-img-container caas-img-loader\" style=\"padding-bottom:56%\"><img alt=\"滙控行政總裁艾橋智。(資料圖片)\" class=\"caas-img caas-lazy has-preview\" data-src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gK_qKHMDFrjzWQcoGiag0w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/cac22953f43f98c4965d7ec776d0844a\"/><noscript><img alt=\"滙控行政總裁艾橋智。(資料圖片)\" class=\"caas-img\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gK_qKHMDFrjzWQcoGiag0w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/cac22953f43f98c4965d7ec776d0844a\"/></noscript></div></div></div><div class=\"caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image\"><figcaption class=\"caption-collapse\">滙控行政總裁艾橋智。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p><span><span><span><span><span>滙豐近年持續調整法國業務佈局，此前已經出售在法國的零售及保險業務。滙控表示，這次裁員旨在加速實施簡化組織架構、使其更加靈活的戰略，以應對不確定的經濟環境，日益激烈的競爭以及昂貴的內部營運成本。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p>原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/滙豐亦裁員-擬裁減法國348個職位-佔當地一成人手/560797?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/滙豐亦裁員-擬裁減法國348個職位-佔當地一成人手/560797?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/滙豐亦裁員-擬裁減法國348個職位-佔當地一成人手/560797?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
